{"tid":1759134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"理工大學嘅保安真係好高質","createTime":"2019-11-27T12:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T07:32:41.000Z","uid":241240,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4cd24b468fb51b2c27895f47ae833c831edbfd","tid":1759134,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"聽講Poly圍城第一日曾經有保安當職<br />\n點解香港人可以咁中意翻工......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我嘅志願都係做學校保安<br />\n但上次約咗三個friend一齊去見工<br />\n最後比佢地放咗飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實當刻我真係好絕望<br />\n但事後諗翻起，都幾慶幸你地冇見到工<br />\n因為我入咗去做之後，真係覺得好痛苦<br />\n放飯得生命麵包，果度啲人根本唔當你人類<br />\n你想偷偷地出去呼吸吓新鮮空即刻比人喝你翻去<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 我一個星期前已經辭咗職，希望你地都過得安好，大家曾經意氣相投，向住同一個夢想進發，好多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f754ffc59d96a3277cc8ccb54e365a53f1ebe7e","tid":1759134,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"祝 安康"},{"pid":"1d6100334abacbe26e75fa3a4adb363341020cbb","tid":1759134,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:28:02.000Z","msg":"我果時一時意氣del曬果三個friend contact<br />\n所以想推到比佢地見到"},{"pid":"36b93b7b97abc95aad007a25d8ac6d14df958b3c","tid":1759134,"uid":241240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"如果你地有咩內疚<br />\n希望你地見到個post"},{"pid":"edd80240115db683911e77c0a4474ea94467801a","tid":1759134,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:39:02.000Z","msg":"同事見到讚一讚呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b369431011c253bfa28bea47ea03884c196409a","tid":1759134,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：我地今鋪無輸的念頭<br />\n<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家80%, 仲差少少</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=dc134598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=9207900d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，雖然區選迎來短暫的勝利，但要做ge 野都要持績落去，唔好放軟手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期四愛丁堡見)"},{"pid":"67e757685108c32cae473090bcf076b92e5ca88e","tid":1759134,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"btw, 理大保安點入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e61bcc7dc537aa032af3b037fc5ba8199259fb","tid":1759134